20.78	Coronagraph	Coronagraph	An optical vortex coronagraph uses a phase-mask in which the phase-shift varies azimuthally around the center. Several varieties of optical vortex coronagraphs exist:	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Cp22liberationdaytransient.png/200px-Cp22liberationdaytransient.png
